Documentation Comment (for projects & APIs)
/** * Name of Project: Online Shopping * Modules: 70 * Project Date: 12th March 2024 * Last Modified: 9th Sep 2025 * Author: James Goling and his friends */

âœ… Summary:

Statically typed â†’ type fixed (C, Java).
Dynamically typed â†’ type flexible (Python, JavaScript).
Comments â†’ make code readable (3 types: single, multi, documentation).
